Text: Sequentially this is show 1 but would more appropriately be labeled S01E00 Pilot (see http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_Offspring_episodes). The smaller release also labeled S01E01 is show 2 but the first episode of season one: in other words, if you want the complete 14 shows of the first "season" you need to download two labeled S01E01, one being twice as large a file as the other. Hope that helps 8)
Thanks for continuing to seed y'all. Never got around to watching this in oz.
